title: Biden wants to be in 2016 race in case 'lightning strikes' Clinton
text: Charles Krauthammer told viewers on “Special Report with Bret Baier” if Vice President Joe Biden decides to run for president, it would be to better ensure a strong Democratic nominee, should political “lightning” strike current primary frontrunner Hillary Clinton. ...
